                  <msItem class="#liturgica" n="1" xml:id="MS_Canon_Liturg_318-item1">
                     <title key="work_10513" type="desc">Book of Hours for private use (?)</title>
                     <rubric>... Officium beate Marie, dicendum cum quindecim antiphonis, psalmis ["spīs"] &amp; orationibus infrascriptis &amp; cum sanctis suis 
                        sexaginta nominibus &amp; letanijs</rubric>
                     <note>Many prayers are added (some in Italian) and St Bernard's Verses ('Illumina oculos',  etc.)</note>
                     <note>The Office is not the ordinary Hours, but a form for private use (?)</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="la" otherLangs="it">Latin and Italian</textLang>
